{"word":"ἐπικίδνημι","slug":"ἐπικίδνημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n39716\" key=\"e)piki/dnhmi\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπικίδνημι</orth>, <sense id=\"n39716.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">spread over</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κακοῖς ἐπικίδνατε θυμόν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">spread</tr_> a brave spirit <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">over</tr_> your ills, Orac. ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:140\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.140</biblScope> </bibl>:—in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram> </gramGrp> (only in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> </bibl>), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὕδωρ ἐπικίδναται ἆιαν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">is spread over</tr_> the earth, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:850\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.850</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:978\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.978</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅσον τ᾽ ἐπικίδναται ἠώς</foreign> far as the morning light <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">is</tr_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\"